VI consider it my life's mission
p4
aVto convey the urgency of climate change through my work.
p5
aVI've traveled north to the Arctic to the capture the unfolding story
p6
aVof polar melt,
p7
aVand south to the Equator to document the subsequent rising seas.
p8
aVMost recently, I visited the icy coast of Greenland
p9
aVand the low-lying islands of the Maldives,
p10
aVconnecting two seemingly disparate but equally endangered
p11
aVparts of our planet.
