aa(lp13
VMy drawings explore moments of transition, turbulence
p14
aVand tranquility in the landscape,
p15
aVallowing viewers to emotionally connect
p16
aVwith a place you might never have the chance to visit.
p17
aVI choose to convey the beauty as opposed to the devastation.
p18
aVIf you can experience the sublimity of these landscapes,
p19
aVperhaps you'll be inspired to protect and preserve them.
